          <title>
            <string language="ca">L'Alt Penedès. Coneguem la comarca.</string>
            <string language="en">L'Alt Penedès. Getting to know the county</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">L'Alt Penedès. Beginnen, die Grafschaft zu
kennen</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">l'Alt Penedès. Finir par connaître le 
comté</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">L'Alt Penedès. Conhecer o condado</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">L'Alt Penedès. Familiarizzazione con la 
contea</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">L'Alt Penedθs. Γνωριμία να είναι γνωστός 
ο νομός</string>
          </title>
          <language>ca</language>
          <description>
            <string language="ca">Unitat didàctica (UD) amb diversos materials per a l'estudi de la comarca de l'Alt Penedès: situació, municipis, relleu, rius i rieres, clima, vegetació, fauna, economia, població, comunicacions, cultura i història.
Conté activitats d'aprenentatge i activitats d'autoavaluació. Presenta mapes muts de la comarca, en blanc i negre, per imprimir. Disposa d'una guia per al professorat i inclou enllaços externs.</string>
            <string language="en">Teaching unit (UD) with different material on the Alt Penedes county: location, towns, relief, rivers and streams, climate, vegetation, fauna, economy, inhabitants, communications, culture and history. It includes learning and self-assessment activities, the possibility of printing blank maps of the region in black and white, a teacher's guide and external links.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="ca">geografia</string>
            <string language="en">geography</string>
            <string language="es">geografía</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="ca">geografia regional</string>
            <string language="en">regional geography</string>
            <string language="es">geografía regional</string>
          </keyword>
          <keyword>
            <string language="ca">Espanya</string>
            <string language="en">Spain</string>
            <string language="es">España</string>
          </keyword>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Unterrichtende Maßeinheit (UD) mit 
unterschiedlichem Material auf der Alt Penedes Grafschaft: 
Standort, Städte, Entlastung, Flüsse und Ströme, Klima, 
Vegetation, Fauna, Wirtschaft, Einwohner, Kommunikationen, Kultur und 
Geschichte. Sie schließt Lernen- und 
Selbstbewertungsaktivitäten, die Möglichkeit des Druckes der 
unbelegten Karten der Region in Schwarzem und in Weißem, die 
Anleitung eines Lehrers und die externen Links ein.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Unité d'enseignement (UD) avec le matériel 
différent sur le comté d'alt Penedes : emplacement, villes, 
soulagement, fleuves et jets, climat, végétation, faune, économie, 
habitants, transmissions, culture et histoire. Il inclut des 
activités d'étude et de art de l'auto-portrait-assessment, la possibilité 
d'imprimer les cartes blanc de la région dans noir et blanc, le guide
d'un professeur et les liens externes.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Unidade ensinando (UD) com material diferente no 
condado do Alt Penedes: posição, cidades, relevo, rios e 
córregos, clima, vegetação, fauna, economia, habitantes, 
comunicações, cultura e history. Inclui atividades da 
aprendizagem e do self-assessment, a possibilidade de imprimir mapas 
em branco da região em preto e em branco, a guia de um professor e as
ligações externas.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Unità d'istruzione (UD) con materiale differente
sulla contea dell'alt Penedes: posizione, città, rilievo, fiumi
e flussi, clima, vegetazione, fauna, economia, abitanti, 
comunicazioni, coltura e storia. Include le attività di 
valutazione di se stesso ed imparare, la possibilità di stampa dei 
programmi in bianco della regione in nero ed in bianco, la guida 
dell'insegnante ed i collegamenti esterni.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Μονάδα (UD) διδασκαλίας με το διαφορετικό υλικό στο
νομό ALT Penedes: θέση, πόλεις, ανακούφιση, ποταμοί 
και ρεύματα, κλίμα, βλάστηση, πανίδα, οικονομία, κάτοικοι, 
επικοινωνίες, πολιτισμός και ιστορία. Περιλαμβάνει τις 
δραστηριότητες εκμάθησης και αυτοαξιολόγησης, τη δυνατότητα τους 
κενούς χάρτες της περιοχής μαύρος και άσπρος, τον οδηγό ενός 
δασκάλου και τις εξωτερικές συνδέσεις.</string>
          </description>
